      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ester, 3-hydroxy-4-{[(3-nitrophenyl)imino]methyl}phenyl tetradecanoate, was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
